<headline>Special Weather Statement issued August 08 at 6:51PM EDT  by NWS Blacksburg</headline>
<description>...A strong thunderstorm will impact portions of central Carroll
County through 730 PM EDT...
At 650 PM EDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm over
Woodlawn, or near Hillsville, moving southeast at 10 mph.
HAZARD...Winds in excess of 30 mph.
SOURCE...Radar indicated.
IMPACT...Gusty winds could knock down tree limbs and blow around
unsecured objects.
Locations impacted include...
Hillsville...
and Woodlawn.
MAX HAIL SIZE...0.00 IN
MAX WIND GUST...30 MPH</description>
<instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
